<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">感覺這個時代比較多都是海洋生物的化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />常聽人家說<delay8 />海洋是萬物之母，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然生命的起源就是大海呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">感覺古代的生物，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />外型看起來都很奇特呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定就是這種有點詭異，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但又有些可愛的模樣，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才擄獲了大家的心吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />各種不同的生物，<delay20 />
最初始的姿態就在這裡<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從這個樣子開始，<delay8 />到底要經歷多少演化，<delay20 />
才能變成現在的模樣呢？<10_4 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊啊！<delay20 />真是充滿古代的浪漫情懷呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="002_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為巨大的化石都很有看頭，<delay20 />
所以我很喜歡喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一走進展覽室，連我這樣成熟的大人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都會壓抑不住內心的興奮呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />恐龍這種大型生物的化石，<delay8 />
就算擺在眼前，<delay20 />也很難令人相信<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來過去曾經存在過這麼巨大的生物。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這種<delay20 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「因為很大，<delay8 />所以很強」的感覺，<delay20 /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
很有古代生物的氛圍，<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常簡單明瞭呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />化石明明就只是生物的骨頭，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />為什麼看起來還是這麼有魄力呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果一直盯著看<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Confused" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得<delay20 />化石好像會動起來一樣，<delay8 />
有點可怕呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="003_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">回過頭去看地球的歷史，<delay8 /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會發現生物們<delay8 />
其實已經面臨過好幾次危機呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是我相信即使如此，<delay8 />只要地球還存在，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就會像這樣，<delay8 />再次出現其他物種，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不斷延續新的生命喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我記得化石應該是從<delay8 />
古老的地層中挖出來的吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />舊的地表不斷累積，<delay20 />
這樣下去<delay8 />地球就會越來越大<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但事實上並不會，很神奇對吧？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是不是還有很多還沒被挖掘出來的<delay20 />
未知生物的化石呢？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />古代世界真是太浪漫了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="100_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想看哪個化石呢？<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就在這裡慢慢看<delay8 />沒關係喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們島上的<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" /><delay8 />看起來怎麼樣？<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比如說化石的展覽方式之類的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得很棒嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="100_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">總覺得一個人來看化石，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好寂寞喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />幸好有你來這裡陪我呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="200_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你不覺得<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />就像是島嶼的一種
特色指標嗎？<delay20 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我沒想到它居然會這麼
氣派，真的嚇了我一跳呢。<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是待在這個莊嚴的空間裡，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就讓我覺得自己的格調<delay8 />
似乎也跟著變高了呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天我是來看化石展覽室的。<delay20 />
總覺得這間房間的陳列<delay8 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人興起<delay8 />無限想像呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />自己住的島上能有<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />，<delay8 />
果然很棒！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="200_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />剛開幕的<colour id="1" />博物館<colour id="65535" />……<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />讓人有各種新發現，真有趣呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是這間房間的照明就很有效果，<delay20 />
我總覺得<anim id="Sleepy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />越來越睏了<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>